    ¿Tienes alguna pregunta o proyecto en mente? ¡Hablemos por WhatsApp!
  </p>
  <a
    href="https://wa.me/51976783049"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 px-4 py-2 bg-white text-black font-bold"
